					name = {"凛", "Rin"},
					"“Well, I’m not a fan of getting my hands dirty. And I did take a video to post on social media later to say, ‘These protestors left so much trash... Disgusting.’ as a psyop. Let’s go, Mizuhiki.”",
					{"rt2"},
